@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yrrwxt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.82
    tmp = (0.42 / (v2 - (v0 + 0.02 * v0 + 0.91)))
    v1 = ((0.77 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.53)) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.58) + (v2 + 0.95 + v1 + 0.36)))
    v0 = 0.28
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.35)) - v2)
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.10 / v1 + 0.30)) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.32) * v2))
    data[tid] = v0
